headline: MAS Q3 Deep Dive: Tariff Headwinds and Industry Softness Impact Results and Outlook
summary: Home-building design and manufacturing company Masco Corporation (NYSE:MAS) fell short of the markets revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025, with sales falling 3.3% year on year to $1.92 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.97 per share was 5.7% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
